How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

3.0 out of 5 stars Only use if you tan easily
Reviewed in the United States on March 26, 2023
Color: Tanning Lotion - SPF 8Size: 8 Fl Oz (Pack of 2)Style: SPF 8Verified Purchase
I really like this product, I use it whenever I go to the beach with my friends. I love the smell of it and it always leaves my skin nice and moisturized afterwards. Something that I have noticed though is that when my fair skinned friend uses this product, she doesn't really tan. She just gets sunburnt. I tan very easily and rarely get sunburnt, and this tanning lotion SPF works wonders for me. I don't know if any other people with light skin have this issue. But overall this product is really nice and I would definitely purchase this again when summer comes rolling around.
